      "description": "Each time a ranged attack targets a ^^**Heretic Astartes**^^ unit from your army (excluding ^^**Damned**^^ units), if the Strength characteristic of that attack is greater than the Toughness characteristic of that unit, subtract 1 from the Wound roll."
