      "description": "Each time a ^^**Heretic Astartes Daemon Vehicle**^^ model from your army makes a Dark Pact, it can invoke its contract. If it does, subtract 1 from the resulting Leadership test when making that Dark Pact and, until the end of the phase:\n- Each time a model in that unit makes a ranged attack, add 1 to the Wound roll.\n- Add 2 to the Attacks characteristic of melee weapons equipped by models in that unit."
