      "description": "Each time an ^^**Emperor's Children**^^ unit from your army is selected to fight, if it made a Charge move this turn, select one of the abilities below. While resolving those attacks, melee weapons equipped by models in that unit have the ability:\n- [^^Lethal Hits^^]\n- [^^Sustained Hits 1^^]"
