    "name": "Purgation Force (Ordo Hereticus)",
    "faction": "Grey Knights",
    "ability": {
      "name": "Root Out Heresy",
      "description": "Ranged weapons equipped by ^^Adeptus Arbites, Inquisitor, Inquisitorial Agents^^ and ^^Ordo Hereticus^^ models from your army have the [IGNORES COVER] ability.\n\n\nEach time an ^^Adeptus Arbites, Inquisitor, Inquisitorial Agents^^ or ^^Ordo Hereticus^^ model from your army makes an attack that targets a ^^Chaos^^ unit containing 5 or more models, that attack has the [SUSTAINED HITS 1] ability."
    },
    "gameSystem": "wh40k-10e"
