      "description": "Each time an ^^Inquisitor, Inquisitorial Agents^^ or ^^Ordo Malleus^^ model from your army makes an attack, re-roll a Hit roll of 1 and, if the target is a ^^Daemon^^ unit, re-roll a Wound roll of 1 as well."
