      "name": "Grim Resolve",
      "description": "While an ^^**Adeptus Astartes**^^ unit from your army is Battle-shocked, change the Objective Control characteristic of models in that unit to 1, instead of 0.\nIn your Command phase, select one ^^**Adeptus Astartes^^** unit from your army; until the start of your next Command phase, add 1 to the Objective Control characteristic of models in that unit."
