      "description": "Each time an Adeptus Astartes unit from your army disembarks from a Transport (excluding Aircraft) that made a Normal or Advance move this phase, that disembarked unit can make a Normal move of up to D6\", or a Normal move of up to D3+3\" instead if that Transport is a Heavy Transport (see below)\n\n\nAdeptus Astartes Transport units from your army (excluding Aircraft) that have a Wounds characteristic of 14+ have the Heavy Transport keyword."
